reviewText:
the tape came in good condition with my collection
thank you

For those who have seen Tenchi before and can't get all the tapes I'd say this is the funniest one!  And for those who have no clue what I'm  talking about when I say this is the greatest, funniest show ever...  Find  out NOW!

First thing I want to say is that the second episode on tistape has NUDITY. So parents please use caution.  There is no sex oranything like that just a few minutes of nudity.  Anyways two more characters are introduced and you learn more about the story behind the series.  You see more about why Ayeka has come to Earth and why Ryoko was in the cave.  You get to see first hand in this tape how Tenchi is going to be *tortured* by these two young beautiful women in his life.  Again a good amount of comedy and story played out.
